text: Soane-Patita Vaimua Lavelua was a king of Uvea, ruling from 1826 to 1829, and again 1830 to 1858. He was preceded at first by Mulitoto, and succeeded by Takala; he succeeded Takala and was later succeeded by Falakika Seilala.
